    "Name": "Reaver RR-S7R",
    "Details": "The Reaver RR-S7R is an 85-ton gladiatorial assault platform built by Firefly Foundry specifically for Solaris VII arena competition. A left-arm Lance serves as the primary melee weapon, supported by a right-torso LB-10X Autocannon carrying both standard and cluster ammunition. The left torso combines an MRM 20 and Large Laser for ranged engagement, while two center-torso Medium Pulse Lasers and a right-arm Fluid Gun round out the close-range arsenal. Dual CASE installations protect both ammunition bays.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Melee Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.15</color></b>",
